data.title: Jiangxi Xingtai Technology Co., Ltd
data.meta_description: Jiangxi Xingtai Technology Co.,ltd, founded in June 2015 with the registered capital of 286million RMB and location , is a one-stop solution provider of EPD（Electronic-Paper Display）integrating RD, design, manufacture and sales as well as assembling of entire machine, headquartered in Industrial Park of Jizhou District, Ji'an City, Jiangxi Province. It’s product has widely applied in smart education, smart transportation, smart medical, smart logistic, smart wearing, smart furniture and other IOT fields. During the rapid development of enterprise, Xingtai also provide the service of full lamination consisting of module, front light and CTP, as well as manufacturing smart hardware, striving to be the industrial leading runner.
data.text:
Established in June 2015 with a registered capital of 286 million yuan, Jiangxi Xingtai Technology Co., Ltd. is located in the Industrial Park of Jizhou District, Ji'an City, Jiangxi Province. As an early enterprise involved in the design, development and manufacture of electronic paper modules, the company is a one-stop service provider for EPD (ElectronicPaperDisplay).
